# ============================================================
# MEDICAL CORE RUNTIME
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: medical
scope: medical.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for medical.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers condition visibility,
intervention state,
recovery state,
historical medical reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- medical context must resolve
- assessment/intervention basis must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid medical context
- invalid intervention basis
- invalid disclosure scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish condition state,
intervention state,
recovery state,
historical reference,
and failure surface.
